T1  - ARCH effects and cointegration: Is the foreign exchange market efficient?
AU  - Alexakis, Panayotis
AU  - Apergis, Nicholas
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 20
IS  - 4
SP  - 687
EP  - 697
PY  - 1996
